”With fondest memories of my dearest son Mark and his dearest wife Frances September 7th 1996

You will Never be Forgotten by all of us who loved you so dearly - AME"¼
®It serves one right; no need to think
It will all be laid before us,
and God will guide us to our graves smiling and singing."
-Bonnie 'Prince' Billy & the Cairo Gang"╣
ČTHOMAS BRAWLEY 03/08/1919 to 31/12/2009
Beloved husband, father & grandfather. Tommy liked to walk daily
round the Park to observe the seasonal changes unfolding.
We enjoyed many happy family hours in his special place.
A wonderful husband and father with great wit and intelligence
he loved his family dearly and we miss him so much.
AGNES BRAWLEY
20th September 1923 to 22nd of March 2013
Much loved Wife, Mother and Grandmother"Š
