╚Anthony Meier 1956 ~ 2012
"We know only too well that what we are doing is nothing more than a
drop in the ocean. But if the drop were not there, the ocean would he missing something". Mother Teresa"Ž
╠BRIAN BOTTING FRICS 1932 2014
First Chairman of the Friends of Battersea Park 1990- 1999
The Hungarian Oak opposite was planted in his memory
A great servant of the Park with a mischievous sense of fun"į
čTo our baby girl
OLIVIA "GASINETTICA" LANDRIAU SARACENT
Who was born sleeping on the 19th of June 2016 at 2.08am
"Out beyond ideas of right and wrong, there is a field
We will meet you there."
Mami & Papa"█
